data.description: . Welcome to your dream home situated near the Deschutes River in the coveted River Meadows community. Discover a beautifully remodeled kitchen, bathrooms, laundry room, brand-new flooring, and freshly painted inside. Enhancing your comfort, you'll find a new dishwasher, a highly efficient whole house attic fan, a tankless water heater, and a newer roof. The kitchen showcases exquisite granite and quartz countertops, complemented by a stylish tile backsplash. The stainless-steel appliances add a touch of sophistication to the space. You'll also have access community amenities, including tennis and pickleball courts, swimming pool, clubhouse, paved paths for leisurely walks, private Deschutes river access, boat/rv storage, and boat launch. Blueprint plans to move the staircase to create a completely open floor plan are included and can be given prior to contract.
